				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">We are magicians... We are supposed to be highly offensive (althought THIS should need fixing), with a big lack of defense.
<br />

<br />
That's how I like to play my mage. 
<br />
Play well and you're god, make a mistake and you're dead. 
<br />

<br />
Yes I think our pets need a boost. 
<br />
Yes I think we shall have a way to reduce our aggro, so we can be offensive (as we're supposed to).
<br />

<br />
But NO, I don't want snare/slow... I want to chain pets, and if I do it bad I get pounded on.
<br />
