				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">&lt;&lt;What's so wrong with this? Druids, Enchanters, Necros all get it.&gt;&gt;
<br />

<br />
Probably because until PoP added "Call of Arch Magi", Mages never had the ability to charm elementals.  Druids, Enchanters and Necros have strong charm lines built into their classes and were capable of charming well before Dire Charm becomes aviable to them as an AA ability.
<br />

<br />
